    • prepararTicket

      public void prepararTicket​(TipoAccion formaProceder)
      Prepares a ticket to be added to the main tickets collection depending on a given TipoAccion indicator.

      On creation a new Ticket instance object is created and populated with the objects which contains the selected options by user in ticket generation window. On update/modification the elementosCine collection in the current Ticket object is cleared to be populated with posibly modified versions, the current chosen client is set on the ticket and the ticket price is recalculated with this posibly new information in the ticket.

      Parameters:
      formaProceder - A TipoAccion enum constant indicator to determine what way to go: creation or modification
      See Also:
      model.Ticket

    • guardianDelGuardado

      public boolean guardianDelGuardado()
      Verifies if exists created tickets that have not been saved in a Cinema Tickets file and sugests to save them.

      Returns false for the following reasons: 

         - There is nothing to save because there are not tickets created 
   - There is nothing to save because the current tickets have already been saved
      Returns true for the following reasons: 
         - There is at least one ticket (or more than one) that has not been saved yet
   - User takes suggestion and decides to save
      Returns:
      A boolean result true or false depending on the conditions mentioned before
